Class PalisadeInputSplit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.InputSplit
      • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.mapreduce.PalisadeInputSplit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

    public class PalisadeInputSplit
extends org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.InputSplit
implements org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable
    The input split for PalisadeInputFormat. This class contains all the information for describing the resources for one split and the necessary connection methods for finding the data services responsible for finding those resources.
